{"tid":1674892,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"至從戒左黨鐵後，有冇人同我一樣愛上左坐巴士","createTime":"2019-10-25T13:16:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T13:21:23.000Z","uid":280659,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"128dcdbf06bcf21900fd4cab16bee482af45095f","tid":1674892,"uid":280659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T13:16:09.000Z","msg":"831後已經無搭過黨鐵<br />\n雖然要用多左成個鐘先番到屋企<br />\n但呢段時間日日搭巴士 睇多左好多野<br />\n以前搭黨鐵淨係識呆坐聽歌<br />\n呢加巴士路途留意多左街邊人同事、咩位置有咩鋪頭，最重要係令我認識多左我既家 - <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"fc334092060377fb2604fe4c464c4b7aa3235c3b","tid":1674892,"uid":280659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T13:19:21.000Z","msg":"罷搭黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f005b4a302d08a3060d960ebe616b2d973c0a5a7","tid":1674892,"uid":280659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T13:21:23.000Z","msg":"坐言起行....我知道等巴士係辛苦，但對比被捕手足！你行多小小一步都唔肯 你唔配做香港人"}]}